System.Data.Linq.SqlClient.Implementation Namespace

Definition

The System.Data.Linq.SqlClient.Implementation namespace contains types that are used for the internal implementation details of a SQL Server provider.

In this Article

Classes

ObjectMaterializer<TDataReader>

Defines methods for dynamically materializing objects.
